title: Old Dominion Performs In Studio! + Raymundo DM’s All 5 CMA 'Best New Artist' Nominees + Lunchbox Upset With Latest 'Croc-Gate' Update
itunes:title: Old Dominion Performs In Studio! + Raymundo DM’s All 5 CMA 'Best New Artist' Nominees + Lunchbox Upset With Latest 'Croc-Gate' Update
description:
Old Dominion stops by the studio to perform a few of their hits and share the stories behind their songs. Raymundo sent Instagram messages to all of the CMA 'Best New Artist' nominees to see who would message back. Luke Combs caused some controversy this week after his team sent pairs of his signature Crocs to some, but not all members of the show. Plus, Bobby found out today that his team has sent yet ANOTHER package to the show...making Lunchbox even that much more upset!
